Package com.fortify.client.ssc.api

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSSCAPI
    Base class for SSC API classes, providing functionality for configuring and accessing the current SSCAuthenticatingRestConnection instance.
    SSCApplicationAPI
    This class is used to access SSC application related functionality.
    SSCApplicationVersionAPI
    This class is used to access SSC application version related functionality.
    SSCApplicationVersionAttributeAPI
    This class is used to access SSC application version attribute related functionality.
    SSCArtifactAPI
    This class is used to access SSC artifact-related functionality.
    SSCAttributeDefinitionAPI
    This class is used to access SSC attribute-related functionality.
    SSCAttributeDefinitionAPI.SSCCreateAttributeDefinitionBuilder  
    SSCAttributeDefinitionAPI.SSCCreateAttributeDefinitionBuilder.SSCAttributeDefinitionOption  
    SSCAuditAssistantAPI
    This class is used to access SSC Audit Assistant related functionality.
    SSCAuthEntityAPI
    This class is used to access SSC application related functionality.
    SSCBugTrackerAPI
    This class is used to access SSC bug tracker related functionality.
    SSCBulkAPI
    This class is used to access the SSC bulk API endpoint.
    SSCBulkAPI.SSCBulkEmbedder
    This class allows for adding extra data to a given JSONList, using a single SSC bulk request to load the extra data for all JSONList entries passed to the SSCBulkAPI.SSCBulkEmbedder.addBulkData(JSONList) method.
    SSCCustomTagAPI
    This class is used to access SSC custom tag related functionality.
    SSCFileUpDownloadAPI
    This class is used to access SSC functionality related to up- and downloading files.
    SSCIssueAPI
    This class is used to access SSC issue-related functionality.
    SSCIssueAPI.IssueSearchOptions
    This class describes the SSC issue search options, allowing to either include or exclude removed, hidden and suppressed issues.
    SSCIssueGroupsAPI
    This class is used to access SSC issue-related functionality.
    SSCIssueTemplateAPI
    This class is used to access SSC issue template related functionality.
    SSCJobAPI
    This class is used to access SSC job-related functionality.
    SSCMetricsAPI
    This class is used to access SSC metrics-related functionality (variables and performance indicators).
    SSCRulepackAPI
    This class is used to access SSC rulepack-related functionality.
